### OP-REPO-02 SUCCESS: exists by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/operators/exists?name=OperatorEntity{{suffix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### OP-REPO-03 SUCCESS: exists by name (ignore case)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/operators/exists/ignorecase?name=operatorentity{{suffix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =============================================================
### - Subscription endpoints
### =============================================================

### SUB-REPO-01 SUCCESS: find subscriptions by user first/last name (ignore case)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/subscriptions/search/userName?name=User{{suffix}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### SUB-REPO-02 SUCCESS: find subscriptions by user id and status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/subscriptions/user/{{userId}}/status?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### SUB-REPO-03 SUCCESS: subscriptions count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/subscriptions/count
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =============================================================
### - User endpoints
### =============================================================

### USER-REPO-01 SUCCESS: exists by email (should be true)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/Users/exists?email={{registeredUserEmail}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### USER-REPO-02 FAIL: exists by email (should be false)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/Users/exists?email=doesnotexist_{{suffix}}@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}




